  o Several small improvements and fixes.
  o G4VSceneHandler: added namespace scope to MeshScoreMap.
- modeling (modeling-V10-05-08):
  o G4CallbackModel: include modeling parameters in passed arguments.
- externals (visexternalgl2ps-V10-05-01):
  o Updated gl2ps sub-module to version 1.4.0.
- OpenGL (OpenGL-V10-05-09):
  o Removed default font size.

